Taipei_Vill= readOGR(dsn=getwd() , layer = "Taipei_Vill", encoding="utf8")
FastFood = readOGR(dsn =getwd(), layer = "Tpe_Fastfood", encoding="utf8")
Taipei_Vill@data$CENSUS=as.numeric(as.character(Taipei_Vill@data$CENSUS))


Taipei_Vill@data$FastFood=poly.counts(FastFood,Taipei_Vill)
Taipei_Vill@data$FFDens=Taipei_Vill@data$FastFood/Taipei_Vill@data$CENSUS*1000
Taipei_Vill.f = fortify(Taipei_Vill, region="VILLAGE")
Taipei_Vill.f = merge(Taipei_Vill.f, Taipei_Vill@data, by.x = "id", by.y = "VILLAGE")

ggplot() + geom_polygon(data =Taipei_Vill.f, aes(x=long, y = lat, group =group,fill =FFDens),color="grey30") + coord_fixed(1.0)+
 scale_fill_gradientn(" \n\n",colors=brewer.pal(7,"YlOrRd"))+
 theme_void()+labs(title ="")+theme(plot.title = element_text(size=18,hjust = 0.5))

Taipei_Town=gUnaryUnion(Taipei_Vill,Taipei_Vill@data$TOWN)
tn_names=names(Taipei_Town)
tn_up=as.vector(poly.counts(subset(FastFood,TYPE_99-TYPE_90>0),Taipei_Town))
tn_zero=as.vector(poly.counts(subset(FastFood,TYPE_99-TYPE_90==0),Taipei_Town))
tn_down=as.vector(poly.counts(subset(FastFood,TYPE_99-TYPE_90<0),Taipei_Town))
a=data.frame(name=tn_names,num=tn_up,lvl="")
b=data.frame(name=tn_names,num=tn_zero,lvl="")
c=data.frame(name=tn_names,num=tn_down,lvl="")
tn_data=rbind(a,b,c)

ggplot(tn_data,aes(x=name,y=num,fill=lvl))+
 geom_bar(stat='identity',position = "stack") +
 scale_fill_manual("",values =c( ""="blue", ""="forestgreen",""="red"),labels = c("","",""))+  theme_minimal()+
 labs(title ="90-99", x = "", y = "")+

Taipei_Town=gUnaryUnion(Taipei_Vill,Taipei_Vill@data$TOWN)
tn_names=names(Taipei_Town)
m_up=as.vector(poly.counts(subset(FastFood,TYPE_99-TYPE_90>0&STORE=="MIC"),Taipei_Town))
k_up=as.vector(poly.counts(subset(FastFood,TYPE_99-TYPE_90>0&STORE=="KFC"),Taipei_Town))
m_zero=as.vector(poly.counts(subset(FastFood,TYPE_99-TYPE_90==0&STORE=="MIC"),Taipei_Town))
k_zero=as.vector(poly.counts(subset(FastFood,TYPE_99-TYPE_90==0&STORE=="KFC"),Taipei_Town))
m_down=as.vector(poly.counts(subset(FastFood,TYPE_99-TYPE_90<0&STORE=="MIC"),Taipei_Town))
k_down=as.vector(poly.counts(subset(FastFood,TYPE_99-TYPE_90<0&STORE=="KFC"),Taipei_Town))
a=data.frame(name=tn_names,num=m_up,lvl="",STORE="MIC")
b=data.frame(name=tn_names,num=k_up,lvl="",STORE="KFC")
c=data.frame(name=tn_names,num=m_zero,lvl="",STORE="MIC")
d=data.frame(name=tn_names,num=k_zero,lvl="",STORE="KFC")
e=data.frame(name=tn_names,num=m_down,lvl="",STORE="MIC")
f=data.frame(name=tn_names,num=k_down,lvl="",STORE="KFC")
t_data=rbind(a,b,c,d,e,f)
t_data$STORE=factor(t_data$STORE,levels=c("MIC","KFC"),labels = c("",""))

ggplot(t_data,aes(x=name,y=num,fill=lvl))+
 facet_grid(.~STORE)+
 geom_bar(stat='identity',position = "stack") +
 scale_fill_manual("",values =c( ""="blue", ""="forestgreen",""="red"),labels = c("","",""))+  theme_minimal()+
 labs(title ="90-99", x = "", y = "")+
 theme(legend.position = "bottom")+theme(plot.title = element_text(size=16,hjust = 0.5))

ggplot(t_data,aes(x=name,y=num,fill=lvl))+
 facet_grid(STORE~., scales = "free_y")+
 geom_bar(stat='identity',position = "stack") +
 scale_fill_manual("",values =c( ""="blue", ""="forestgreen",""="red"),labels = c("","",""))+  theme_minimal()+
 labs(title ="90-99", x = "", y = "")+
 theme(legend.position = "bottom")+theme(plot.title = element_text(size=16,hjust = 0.5))

Taipei_TOWN.f <- fortify(Taipei_Vill, region="TOWN")
Taipei_TOWN.f <- merge(Taipei_TOWN.f, Taipei_Vill@data, by.x = "id", by.y = "TOWN")

mic=FastFood@data[FastFood@data$STORE=="MIC",]
mic_x=mic$X_COOR;mic_y=mic$Y_COOR
mic_lvl=mic$TYPE_99-mic$TYPE_90
mic_lvl[mic_lvl>0]="";mic_lvl[mic_lvl==0]="";mic_lvl[mic_lvl<0]=""
mic_lvl=factor(mic_lvl,levels=c("","",""))

ggplot()+
 geom_polygon(data =Taipei_TOWN.f, aes(x=long, y = lat, group = group), fill="khaki1", color="black") + 
 geom_point(aes(x=mic_x,y=mic_y,color=factor(mic_lvl)),shape=19,size=2) +scale_color_manual("",values =c( "blue", "forestgreen","red"))+coord_fixed(1.0)+
 scale_x_continuous(labels =NULL,name =NULL )+  scale_y_continuous(labels =NULL,name =NULL )+
 theme_void()+labs(title ="90-99")+
 theme(legend.position = "bottom")+theme(plot.title = element_text(size=16,hjust = 0.5))
